{"tid":1934182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求指教  懷疑買到含有甲醇嘅消毒酒精","createTime":"2020-03-19T18:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T12:28:09.000Z","uid":161000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7182edb5fb369cd2c7c054a3c87dd66e47291f51","tid":1934182,"uid":161000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"代朋友po<br />\n小弟早係疫情爆發前就係天水圍 天盛某藥房買左兩枝消毒酒精<br />\n喺3月又再買多三枝消毒酒精。不過就好奇點解價錢係同疫情爆發前個時一樣，所以就膽操操搵左甲醇檢測用嘅工具<br />\n利申 無chem底 剩係跟說明書指示 <br />\ntest左5樣野嘅 <br />\n1) 清水 <br />\n2) 小弟自家釀嘅酒(失敗嘅) <br />\n3)消毒酒精(疫情爆發前) <br />\n4)消毒酒精(疫情爆發後) <br />\n5)消毒酒精(疫情爆發後)<br />\n結果如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCfpmnb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCfpmnb.jpg&h=7065e410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清水完全無事，自家釀嘅酒可能有少少，其他三枝都奶撚哂野<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7RhGoAw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RhGoAw.jpg&h=6cce1e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 想問咁多位巴打個甲醇含量係唔係好高 仲用唔用得?"},{"pid":"dd90f8a3fb2ccae275869aff94800286a145d112","tid":1934182,"uid":161000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T18:43:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfb69eb04bebaf6990d0557d44f86ef26631c076","tid":1934182,"uid":161000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T18:43:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30d48cee043651577c4312a025c0563ea37b49cf","tid":1934182,"uid":161000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T18:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a982c2394d07f3cea8cd338b1b9f2bb1962582","tid":1934182,"uid":336645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T18:44:46.000Z","msg":"中國牌子？"},{"pid":"1b4fba5020d08b5edd5139eaef5966019d36c8e1","tid":1934182,"uid":161000,"like":0,"dislike